  "details": "\n---\n_-= Per source details. Do not edit below this line.=-_\n\n## Source: amazon-inspector (aa4d6837b829b5ed3ef1fcd1f0bf65919df53b2c02c96e7b2c63dbc3e41b965c)\nThe package was found to contain malicious code or consuming dependency that contains malicious code\n\n## Source: kam193 (6ebd6a0497e01ef631a2c357263bd1af23d88e8d9a9ae46fe39110571949198c)\nDuring import, the package starts a reverse shell\n\n\n---\n\nCategory: MALICIOUS - The campaign has clearly malicious intent, like infostealers.\n\n\nCampaign: 2026-06-anthropy\n\n\nReasons (based on the campaign):\n\n\n - The package contains code to create a reverse shell, allowing an attacker to execute any commands on the victim's machine.\n",
